:Energy_efficient_Building_Units rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                 rdfs:subClassOf :Operational_Energy_Efficiency ;
                                 rdfs:DescribestheReason "Energy-efficient Building Units: To decrease the operational energy consumption (saving energy)." .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/besenyo/ontologies/2021/10/untitled-ontology-21#Energy_efficient_Heating_and_Cooling
:Energy_efficient_Heating_and_Cooling rdf:type owl:Class ;
