:Energy_efficient_Lighting rdf:type owl:Class ;
                           rdfs:subClassOf :Operational_Energy_Efficiency ;
                           rdfs:DescribestheReason """Energy-efficient Lighting: 
To decrease the operational energy consumption, by de-lamping, raplacing lamps of harvesting natural day light (saving energy).""" .


